data.description: Stepless Ranch! Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroomed, 2-bathroom home that sits on over a half-acre of land!  Your private owner's suite features a large bath with separate shower and tub, and a large walk-in closet.  The home has a huge bonus room perfect for a home office, recreation use, etc.  Covered back patio for quiet evening.  There is a storage shed with a roll-up door.      This home is perfect for entertaining and gardening.
